1. GNOME Terminal
2. Vim
3. Plugins for specific languages

1. GNOME Terminal:
(Tab creation/deletion)
Ctrl+alt+n 'new tab'
ctrl+alt+k 'kill tab'

(Navigation)
ctrl+h 'move to the tab to the left'
ctrl+l 'move to the tab to the right'
ctrl+/ 'search'
ctrl+n 'next'

2. Vim
fj 'auto indent the entire file'
ctrl+(hjkl) to 'switch around the Vims inside a same terminal'

3. Plugins for specific languages
Typescript: https://github.com/leafgarland/typescript-vim
